# Web service setup
To enable communication between LS Express and the fiscal printer, two specific web services must be added.
It is therefore necessary to publish the following codeunits:
* 70624157 "EOS081FiscalReceiptWS"
* 70624158 "EOS081ZReportReceiptWS"

